A Tango Delta©® Feautured map made by: Rootbeerz Xfire: doctorgunpowder AIM: md123ran Email: mattsplace@sbcglobal.net de_deepswine Overview - The terrorist have escaped the prison, and buried the gaurds in the gound. The counter-terrorists have just arrived to clear out the threats. Terrorist - Wipe out the opposing team or either blow up the railroad or the skywalk. Counter-terrorist - Wipe out the threats or defuse the bomb. Tips - Snipers can be up in the tower, be sure to use smokes while moving in open spaces. Use shadows to your advantage.
